#: admin/partials/bp-edit-activities-faq.php:28
msgid "What is BuddyPress Edit Activity?"
msgstr ""

#: admin/partials/bp-edit-activities-faq.php:32
msgid "BuddyPress Edit Activity is a plugin that allows users to edit their activity posts and comments directly from the frontend of your BuddyPress-powered site. It helps maintain content accuracy and improves user engagement."
msgstr ""

#: admin/partials/bp-edit-activities-faq.php:41
msgid "Can users edit their activity posts sitewide?"
msgstr ""

#: admin/partials/bp-edit-activities-faq.php:45
msgid "Yes, users can edit their posts in the Sitewide Activity Stream, Single Group Pages, and User Activity Pages, ensuring their shared content remains relevant and up-to-date."
msgstr ""

#: admin/partials/bp-edit-activities-faq.php:54
msgid "How long can users edit their activity posts?"
msgstr ""

#: admin/partials/bp-edit-activities-faq.php:58
msgid "Administrators can configure the editing duration with options such as Forever, 30 Days, 7 Days, 1 Day, 1 Hour, or 10 minutes, allowing flexible control over post modifications."
msgstr ""

#: admin/partials/bp-edit-activities-faq.php:67
msgid "Can users edit activity comments?"
msgstr ""

#: admin/partials/bp-edit-activities-faq.php:71
msgid "Yes, users can edit their own comments on activity posts, just like they can edit the posts themselves, ensuring accuracy in conversations and community discussions."
msgstr ""

#: admin/partials/bp-edit-activities-faq.php:80
msgid "Does the plugin work with BuddyPress Groups?"
msgstr ""

#: admin/partials/bp-edit-activities-faq.php:84
msgid "Yes, BuddyPress Edit Activity allows users to edit their posts within BuddyPress Groups, enabling better collaboration and accurate discussions within group activity feeds."
msgstr ""

#: admin/partials/bp-edit-activities-faq.php:94
msgid "Does this plugin support other BuddyPress add-ons?"
msgstr ""

#: admin/partials/bp-edit-activities-faq.php:98
msgid "Yes, BuddyPress Edit Activity seamlessly integrates with BuddyPress Check-ins, BuddyPress Quotes, BuddyPress Status, BuddyPress Giphy, and BuddyPress Polls, allowing users to modify check-ins, quotes, status updates, GIFs, and poll details after posting."
msgstr ""

#: admin/partials/bp-edit-activities-faq.php:107
msgid "How do users edit an activity post?"
msgstr ""

#: admin/partials/bp-edit-activities-faq.php:111
msgid "Users can locate their post in the activity stream or user profile, click the Edit button next to the post, make the necessary changes, and click Update Activity to save the edits."
msgstr ""

